reviewtext: My Flip Video Ultra Series Camcorder wouldn't connect using this cable.  I purchased a Flip Video Ultra Series Camcorder along with this Belkin F3U134-10 USB Extension Cable.  My computer (Dell running XP Pro) wouldn't recognize the USB device (Flip Ultra) using this cable.  The Flip connected immediately when plugged directly into the USB port.Belkin is a reputable supplier but this cable got just 1 star for my application.
summary: Flip Video Ultra Series Camcorder wouldn't connect...
